trans-unit.source: Specifies the input bin that is used as the source of blank paper or other print media.
trans-unit.target: Angir inndata biters som brukes som kilde tomme eller andre Skriv ut mediet.

trans-unit.source: The values of this type are used primarily for these purposes: - As members of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.InputBinCapability%2A> collection, a property of <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>, they indicate the types of input bins that the printer supports.
trans-unit.target: Verdiene for denne typen brukes først og fremst for dette formålet: – som medlemmer av den <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.InputBinCapability%2A>samling, en egenskap for <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>, de angir typer inndata intervaller som skriveren støtter.</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> </xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.InputBinCapability%2A>

trans-unit.source: - As the value of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.InputBin%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>, they instruct the printer to use the specified bin.
trans-unit.target: -Som verdien for den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.InputBin%2A>for en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>, de be skriver for å bruke den angitte posisjon.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.InputBin%2A>

trans-unit.source: The Unknown value is never used in properties of <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> objects.
trans-unit.target: Ukjent verdi aldri er brukt i Egenskaper for <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>objekter.</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>

trans-unit.source: You should never set a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> property to Unknown.
trans-unit.target: Du må angi aldri en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>egenskapen ukjent.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: If some other <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> producing application has created a PrintTicket document that sets the input bin feature to an unrecognized option, (that is, an option that is not defined in the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397), then a <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> object in your application that is constructed with that document will have Unknown as the value of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.InputBin%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis noen andre <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>produserer applikasjonen er opprettet et PrintTicket-dokument som angir funksjonen inndata posisjon til et ugjenkjennelig alternativ (som er et alternativ som ikke er definert i det [Skriv ut skjemaet](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397), og deretter en <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>objektet i programmet som er laget med dette dokumentet har ukjent som verdien for det <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.InputBin%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket.InputBin%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: Although the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> classes cannot be inherited, you can extend the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397) to recognize print device features that are not accounted for in the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> or <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> classes.
trans-unit.target: Selv om den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>og <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>klasser kan arves, kan du utvide den [skrive ut skjemaet](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397) ikke gjenkjenne skriver funksjoner som ikke blir inkludert i den <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>eller <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>klasser.</xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> </xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> </xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [NOTINBUILD: How to: Extend the Print Schema and Create New Print System Classes](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a3600218-1ea5-478a-9853-6560464f2885).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [NOTINBUILD: slik: utvide Skriv ut skjemaet og opprette nye utskrift systemklasser](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/a3600218-1ea5-478a-9853-6560464f2885).
